WEBVTT

01:25.920 --> 01:34.990
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.450 --> 01:37.960
[Episode 17]

01:40.780 --> 01:44.250
Dad had this brought to us.

01:45.120 --> 01:47.430
He misses us.

01:47.870 --> 01:49.990
Hongmei, Zongbao said

01:50.180 --> 01:52.300
he wouldn't wire the money this time.

01:52.620 --> 01:54.430
He heard I was coming back,

01:54.920 --> 01:55.650
so he asked me

01:55.789 --> 01:57.320
to bring it to you directly.

02:07.640 --> 02:09.080
Uncle Wang, my mom is asking

02:09.080 --> 02:11.520
if my dad has many acting jobs in Beijing

02:11.680 --> 02:13.340
and if he's tired from acting.

02:17.240 --> 02:19.040
Yes, he has loads of acting jobs.

02:19.250 --> 02:21.340
Your dad is quite a busy man.

02:23.579 --> 02:24.110
Xiaobao!

02:25.000 --> 02:26.500
Look at this. Look.

02:26.630 --> 02:27.970
Look what your dad bought you—

02:27.970 --> 02:29.430
Beijing local specialties.

02:29.430 --> 02:30.680
Look. What is this?

02:31.310 --> 02:32.210
Tuckahoe cake.

02:33.090 --> 02:34.020
What is this?

02:34.650 --> 02:36.010
Preserved fruit.

02:36.250 --> 02:37.380
And what about this?

02:38.210 --> 02:40.010
Eight Beijing-style Pastries.

02:40.930 --> 02:42.079
Everyone who has been

02:42.079 --> 02:43.610
to Beijing would buy these.

02:43.970 --> 02:44.620
Your dad

02:44.630 --> 02:45.360
went from shop to shop

02:45.360 --> 02:46.800
to buy you every famous specialty.

02:46.800 --> 02:47.600
He also told me

02:47.620 --> 02:48.680
to keep them

02:48.680 --> 02:50.340
from being crushed on the way.

02:52.360 --> 02:52.890
Hongmei.

02:53.750 --> 02:56.450
Zongbao is very frugal.

02:56.530 --> 02:57.130
Look.

02:57.250 --> 02:59.650
He couldn't bear to throw away
these old clothes,

02:59.650 --> 03:00.400
saying

03:00.930 --> 03:03.730
that they should be kept
for working in the fields.

03:04.910 --> 03:06.970
I didn't have much luggage this time,

03:07.020 --> 03:09.470
so I brought these things back with me.

03:09.800 --> 03:11.200
It saved postage as well.

03:12.400 --> 03:13.190
Listen,

03:13.810 --> 03:14.740
Zongbao asked me

03:15.150 --> 03:16.960
to bring you two to reunite with him
in Beijing

03:16.960 --> 03:18.940
when I go back there in a few days.

03:21.000 --> 03:22.060
I have things to do.

03:22.579 --> 03:23.500
I need to leave now.

03:23.500 --> 03:24.700
I've got things to do.

03:24.960 --> 03:26.360
I'll walk Uncle Wang out.

03:26.690 --> 03:27.800
I'll walk Uncle Wang out, Mom.

03:27.800 --> 03:28.930
No need to see me off!

03:29.960 --> 03:30.900
Stop there!

03:58.190 --> 03:59.150
Uncle Wang,

03:59.800 --> 04:01.860
what roles does my dad act in Beijing?

04:01.970 --> 04:03.900
Does he still play the guerrillas?

04:05.090 --> 04:07.000
Yes, he plays any kind of role.

04:07.280 --> 04:09.180
He acts in whatever pays him most.

04:09.750 --> 04:12.080
During these years
my dad spent in Beijing,

04:12.080 --> 04:14.280
he keeps talking about acting in shows.

04:14.470 --> 04:16.120
But why haven't I seen him

04:16.300 --> 04:18.029
in any drama or movie even once?

04:18.690 --> 04:20.750
All my classmates say I'm just lying.

04:21.100 --> 04:22.100
Also, Uncle Wang,

04:22.250 --> 04:23.850
just now when my mom asked you

04:23.860 --> 04:26.550
if my dad was tired from acting
in Beijing,

04:27.130 --> 04:28.860
why did you suddenly freeze up?

04:31.390 --> 04:32.070
Kid,

04:33.130 --> 04:35.040
there's no job that isn't tiring.

04:36.370 --> 04:37.630
Do you think money in Beijing

04:37.630 --> 04:38.800
grows on trees,

04:39.180 --> 04:40.450
that you can reach it with your arms

04:40.450 --> 04:41.710
or bend down to pick it?

04:43.920 --> 04:45.130
When you grow up,

04:46.480 --> 04:47.680
you will understand.

04:48.390 --> 04:49.190
In the future,

04:50.130 --> 04:51.730
you must treat your dad well.

04:52.420 --> 04:53.350
I'm leaving now.

05:13.270 --> 05:14.390
Mom, Mom.

05:53.870 --> 05:54.870
Morning, Ms. Yue.

06:04.630 --> 06:06.160
Lucy, wait a minute.

06:06.310 --> 06:06.910
Come here.

06:08.510 --> 06:09.180
Do a spin.

06:12.250 --> 06:13.070
This sweater of yours

06:13.070 --> 06:14.330
doesn't seem to be from any brand.

06:14.330 --> 06:15.460
Where did you buy it?

06:15.560 --> 06:16.830
I designed it myself

06:16.890 --> 06:18.420
and had my mom make it for me.

06:18.830 --> 06:20.360
You can do design drawings?

06:20.920 --> 06:21.430
Oh right.

06:21.430 --> 06:22.540
One of today's design drawings

06:22.540 --> 06:23.470
was done by Lucy.

06:25.810 --> 06:26.470
Take a seat.

06:26.510 --> 06:27.000
Okay.

06:31.680 --> 06:33.280
Alright. Let's get started.

06:33.600 --> 06:34.190
Ms. Yue,

06:34.480 --> 06:35.360
these are Team No. 1's

06:35.360 --> 06:35.890
designs.

06:35.920 --> 06:36.980
Please take a look.

06:38.810 --> 06:41.980
[Designer: Tracy]

06:49.430 --> 06:50.270
Oh right, Toby,

06:50.270 --> 06:51.120
later on, make me

06:51.120 --> 06:51.870
a drawing

06:51.920 --> 06:53.130
of Lucy's sweater.

06:55.740 --> 06:56.450
Got it.

06:59.130 --> 06:59.750
Ms. Yue,

06:59.800 --> 07:01.530
the first two designs are mine.

07:03.650 --> 07:04.990
[Designer: Toby]

07:05.010 --> 07:06.980
[Designer: Toby]

07:07.010 --> 07:07.920
Nice designs.

07:08.500 --> 07:09.760
You've made progress.

07:10.130 --> 07:10.720
Not bad.

07:12.040 --> 07:12.630
You guys

07:12.630 --> 07:14.160
should all learn from Toby.

07:17.320 --> 07:19.350
[Designer: Lucy]

07:22.510 --> 07:23.220
[Designer: Lucy]

07:23.250 --> 07:25.010
This drawing of Lucy's is confirmed.

07:25.010 --> 07:26.060
Just make the garment

07:26.060 --> 07:27.660
after touching up the lines.

07:31.980 --> 07:32.640
Dismissed.

07:45.360 --> 07:46.060
Ms. Yue,

07:46.800 --> 07:47.800
I'd like to ask...

07:48.330 --> 07:48.870
are you sure

07:48.870 --> 07:50.180
about using my design?

07:50.500 --> 07:51.570
Didn't you hear me

07:51.600 --> 07:52.950
assigning tasks just now?

07:52.950 --> 07:54.040
I just found it...

07:54.620 --> 07:55.860
a bit unbelievable.

07:56.330 --> 07:57.850
Is there anything I need to do?

07:57.850 --> 08:00.250
This concludes your design work this time.

08:04.070 --> 08:05.070
Now, give me a pen.

08:14.560 --> 08:16.050
[Designer: Yue Ru]

08:19.810 --> 08:20.810
Ms. Yue, this...

08:24.770 --> 08:25.680
Silly girl.

08:28.010 --> 08:29.120
Five minutes ago,

08:29.870 --> 08:31.470
this drawing was worthless.

08:32.110 --> 08:32.940
But now,

08:33.600 --> 08:34.799
because of this name,

08:35.220 --> 08:36.600
this drawing will produce at least

08:36.600 --> 08:38.659
hundreds of thousands yuan in sales.

08:38.820 --> 08:41.280
That's called personal value. Understood?

08:41.390 --> 08:42.650
You made a good design.

08:42.870 --> 08:44.070
Keep up the good work.

08:44.500 --> 08:46.360
Welcome to the real world.

08:51.650 --> 08:52.220
Toby!

08:52.870 --> 08:54.000
Meet me in my office.

08:54.910 --> 08:55.550
Keep it up.

09:09.480 --> 09:10.280
Wait a minute.

09:11.410 --> 09:11.980
How come I feel

09:11.980 --> 09:13.380
you're different today?

09:13.790 --> 09:14.850
How am I different?

09:15.320 --> 09:16.510
You used to be passionate

09:16.510 --> 09:17.770
about every audition.

09:18.270 --> 09:18.910
Why do you look like

09:18.910 --> 09:20.170
a wilted flower today?

09:20.740 --> 09:22.270
You look utterly listless.

09:22.320 --> 09:23.470
This won't do.

09:25.410 --> 09:28.340
Mr. Cui, how many times
have I been through this?

09:29.320 --> 09:31.150
I'll just be there to fill the space.

09:31.150 --> 09:32.610
The second female lead...

09:32.840 --> 09:34.840
Is that something I dare to dream of?

09:34.870 --> 09:36.940
But today... things are different.

09:37.100 --> 09:38.900
How are things different today?

09:39.790 --> 09:40.500
Mr. Cui,

09:40.770 --> 09:42.620
now I finally get it.

09:43.010 --> 09:44.660
In fact, many things

09:44.910 --> 09:46.440
have already been decided.

09:46.670 --> 09:48.330
Besides, I'm not good enough.

09:48.410 --> 09:50.110
I'm not very pretty

09:50.200 --> 09:51.820
or experienced in acting.

09:53.200 --> 09:56.290
And I can never cross the boundary
in my heart.

09:57.980 --> 09:58.440
Mr. Cui,

09:58.460 --> 10:00.440
please don't be mad
about what I just said.

10:00.440 --> 10:02.550
I am actually very grateful to you,

10:03.620 --> 10:04.870
for giving me so many opportunities

10:04.870 --> 10:05.860
and so much help.

10:06.150 --> 10:07.370
Too bad that I've seized none of them

10:07.370 --> 10:09.500
and always let your effort go to waste.

10:10.510 --> 10:13.290
Have you... not seized a chance?

10:14.130 --> 10:15.590
What chance have I seized?

10:20.650 --> 10:21.770
We're going to be late.

10:21.770 --> 10:23.220
Let's go upstairs now.

10:23.220 --> 10:24.480
Mr. Cui, rest assured.

10:24.620 --> 10:27.950
Even if it's just a formality,
I'll still take it seriously.

10:35.870 --> 10:36.890
The issue with these pleats...

10:36.890 --> 10:37.550
Toby!

10:37.940 --> 10:38.360
Come over.

10:38.360 --> 10:38.820
Coming.

10:39.290 --> 10:41.020
Get it to me by the end of the day.

10:41.440 --> 10:42.100
Toby.

10:45.460 --> 10:46.060
What's up?

10:46.080 --> 10:46.880
Where is Toby?

10:47.700 --> 10:48.560
He just went by.

10:48.840 --> 10:49.850
No, I mean...

10:50.320 --> 10:50.980
Oh, that Toby.

10:50.980 --> 10:52.380
Ms. Yu fired him that day.

10:53.390 --> 10:54.330
Just out of blue?

10:54.870 --> 10:55.510
Why?

10:56.250 --> 10:56.840
He was practically

10:56.840 --> 10:58.480
a great contributor to the company.

10:58.480 --> 11:00.050
Two mere failed designs

11:00.510 --> 11:01.710
led to his dismissal.

11:02.010 --> 11:03.700
But many of his designs
were approved before.

11:03.700 --> 11:04.840
Are you silly or what?

11:04.840 --> 11:07.100
Could the approved designs still be his?

11:22.240 --> 11:22.960
Ms. Yue,

11:23.870 --> 11:24.770
there's one thing

11:24.770 --> 11:26.370
I'd like to discuss with you.

11:27.390 --> 11:27.960
Go ahead.

11:30.460 --> 11:30.940
I know

11:30.940 --> 11:33.170
your name contains great value.

11:34.120 --> 11:34.620
But I am

11:34.620 --> 11:36.680
the original creator of this design.

11:36.820 --> 11:38.670
So, I'm wondering if it's possible

11:38.670 --> 11:40.200
to put my name after yours.

11:43.220 --> 11:44.460
Do you think your name

11:44.550 --> 11:45.500
can be put side to side

11:45.500 --> 11:46.650
with mine?

11:48.510 --> 11:49.670
As far as I know,

11:50.020 --> 11:51.010
all designs,

11:51.010 --> 11:53.140
be they big or small, are copyrighted.

11:53.550 --> 11:54.980
Given that, in this regard,

11:54.980 --> 11:55.710
you and I are

11:55.940 --> 11:57.400
entitled to equal rights.

11:57.530 --> 11:58.500
Theoretically, yes.

11:57.890 --> 12:06.670
[Costume Design]

12:00.620 --> 12:01.550
What do you mean?

12:04.150 --> 12:06.030
Theoretically, we are equal.

12:06.730 --> 12:08.100
But if you continue to let

12:08.100 --> 12:09.560
such idealistic theories

12:09.870 --> 12:11.120
guide every aspect

12:11.120 --> 12:12.320
of your work and life,

12:12.600 --> 12:14.060
you'll be in sheer misery.

12:14.360 --> 12:16.560
But this is not an argument of theories.

12:16.700 --> 12:17.860
I'm just fighting for

12:17.860 --> 12:19.190
the rights I deserve.

12:20.010 --> 12:21.470
The rights you deserve...

12:21.890 --> 12:23.090
How do you prove that?

12:24.050 --> 12:25.410
You did the drawing
with the company's resources

12:25.410 --> 12:26.610
during office hours.

12:27.240 --> 12:27.860
Your manuscript

12:27.860 --> 12:29.390
is saved on a company-owned computer.

12:29.390 --> 12:30.770
But the idea and the core design

12:30.770 --> 12:31.530
are both mine.

12:31.530 --> 12:32.980
-This is my own creation.
-Okay.

12:32.980 --> 12:33.880
Lucy, stop.

12:34.340 --> 12:35.530
I'm now taking two minutes

12:35.530 --> 12:36.860
to say these words to you

12:37.150 --> 12:37.940
simply because

12:37.940 --> 12:38.940
a friend of mine

12:39.010 --> 12:40.090
made a call to me,

12:40.500 --> 12:41.270
saying that a friend of his

12:41.270 --> 12:42.170
would like to recommend someone

12:42.170 --> 12:43.020
to my company.

12:43.600 --> 12:45.390
For me, your personal value

12:45.500 --> 12:46.440
is entirely built on

12:46.440 --> 12:48.970
the value
of those two acquaintances of mine,

12:49.320 --> 12:50.450
but not on yourself.

12:51.330 --> 12:51.770
You...

12:52.270 --> 12:53.330
amount to nothing.

12:55.010 --> 12:56.050
I do call your name every day.

12:56.050 --> 12:56.860
But so what?

12:56.960 --> 12:58.690
Is your name worth even a penny?

12:58.770 --> 13:00.540
My company has shareholders.

13:01.460 --> 13:03.460
Suppose one day I did a terrible job,

13:03.550 --> 13:04.410
the board would

13:04.460 --> 13:06.120
strike my name off at 8:00 a.m.,

13:06.120 --> 13:06.720
and a new boss

13:06.720 --> 13:08.150
would be here at 10:00 a.m.

13:08.150 --> 13:09.700
Even the morning meeting
would happen as usual.

13:09.700 --> 13:11.290
This is called "the mechanism of society."

13:11.290 --> 13:12.020
Understood?

13:13.200 --> 13:14.220
It was because I realized this

13:14.220 --> 13:15.270
in the early years

13:15.500 --> 13:17.360
that I could become who I am today.

13:27.200 --> 13:28.910
Chinese characters have profound depth.

13:28.910 --> 13:31.310
There's also a phrase called "social ill."

13:31.440 --> 13:32.640
Ms. Yue, I don't think

13:32.910 --> 13:33.580
you should disguise

13:33.580 --> 13:35.440
concessions as personal growth.

13:35.960 --> 13:36.760
In my opinion,

13:37.480 --> 13:38.580
real growth means

13:39.240 --> 13:40.370
to use one's own ability

13:40.370 --> 13:41.460
to fight for more opportunities

13:41.460 --> 13:43.120
to avoid making concessions.

13:43.510 --> 13:45.360
Though I'm only doing an ordinary job,

13:45.360 --> 13:46.050
I don't see the necessity

13:46.050 --> 13:46.820
of treating myself

13:46.820 --> 13:48.750
as a dispensable supporting role.

13:50.000 --> 13:51.730
Every task I complete with care

13:52.220 --> 13:52.860
is experience

13:52.860 --> 13:55.520
for the ideal role I aspire to play
in the future.

14:01.450 --> 14:03.760
[Costume Design]

14:04.620 --> 14:06.480
Thank you for taking time with me.

14:07.870 --> 14:09.820
No need to pay me for the internship.

14:09.820 --> 14:11.270
But this design drawing...

14:11.270 --> 14:12.330
will leave with me.

14:21.400 --> 14:23.080
[Employee ID: Lucy]

14:26.600 --> 14:31.650
[Bulletin Board]

14:27.370 --> 14:28.010
It's freezing cold.

14:28.010 --> 14:29.470
Maybe just don't eat that?

14:30.000 --> 14:31.890
I need this ice pop to help me calm down.

14:31.890 --> 14:33.170
Isn't the air cold enough to calm you down

14:33.170 --> 14:34.230
without an ice pop?

14:35.960 --> 14:36.750
I quit my job.

14:39.720 --> 14:41.120
Y-You quit your job?

14:46.250 --> 14:47.780
Then I need to calm down too.

14:51.360 --> 14:52.580
I did resign, for real.

14:52.580 --> 14:52.940
Well,

14:52.940 --> 14:54.290
there must be a reason.

14:55.550 --> 14:56.620
Yesterday,

14:57.240 --> 14:58.770
I was really happy at first,

14:58.870 --> 14:59.790
thinking that Ms. Yue

14:59.790 --> 15:01.250
finally picked my design.

15:01.790 --> 15:04.380
But before I could savor the moment,

15:04.700 --> 15:05.580
she crossed out

15:05.580 --> 15:06.360
my name

15:06.500 --> 15:07.740
and put hers on it,

15:08.390 --> 15:09.130
claiming only that

15:09.130 --> 15:10.730
could put value to my design.

15:11.650 --> 15:13.010
In the end, she even said I was nothing.

15:13.010 --> 15:14.490
She must be crazy!

15:15.750 --> 15:17.750
She's really insane. Just ignore her.

15:17.750 --> 15:19.530
She not only crossed out your name,

15:19.530 --> 15:21.630
but also attempted to use your design.

15:21.630 --> 15:22.250
Smart move quitting that job.

15:21.940 --> 15:25.540
[End-of-term Performance
of Beijing Conservatory of Music]

15:22.360 --> 15:24.220
If I were you, I would've quit too.

15:24.650 --> 15:25.720
What an awful person,

15:25.720 --> 15:27.650
for doing such a thing as a teacher.

15:28.080 --> 15:29.700
Gold shines wherever it is.

15:30.500 --> 15:30.960
Right?

15:31.460 --> 15:32.460
D-Don't be upset.

15:33.370 --> 15:35.290
To have my creations properly used,

15:35.290 --> 15:36.740
I must become a boss in the future.

15:36.740 --> 15:38.270
You have my support on that!

15:38.290 --> 15:39.010
On top of that,

15:39.010 --> 15:39.810
I also believe

15:40.290 --> 15:41.150
you will have

15:41.510 --> 15:42.530
your own costume design company

15:42.530 --> 15:44.330
as long as you set your mind to it.

15:44.630 --> 15:45.980
Then if I become a boss one day,

15:45.980 --> 15:47.130
you must work as my advisor.

15:47.130 --> 15:48.200
No problem.

15:48.200 --> 15:48.690
We...

15:48.720 --> 15:50.360
will absolutely not bully young people.

15:50.360 --> 15:52.030
And we must respect their creativity!

15:52.030 --> 15:53.130
We'll give them high salaries.

15:53.130 --> 15:54.130
And treat them to coffee!

15:54.130 --> 15:55.190
Most importantly,

15:55.250 --> 15:56.100
we will respect

15:56.100 --> 15:57.700
everyone's fruits of labor.

16:05.370 --> 16:06.270
Does it seem to be

16:06.270 --> 16:07.470
too big a dream for us?

16:07.960 --> 16:08.790
How is that big?

16:08.790 --> 16:09.740
It's our own dream.

16:09.740 --> 16:11.170
We can make whatever dream we want.

16:11.170 --> 16:13.030
It might come true one day, right?

16:13.200 --> 16:14.000
Yes, it might.

16:16.030 --> 16:17.290
Originally, I thought

16:17.630 --> 16:19.440
I could learn and make money there

16:19.440 --> 16:21.500
at the same time to pay my lesson fees.

16:23.080 --> 16:24.480
Was my quitting an impulsive move?

16:24.480 --> 16:25.680
How was it impulsive?

16:25.790 --> 16:27.390
It was not an impulsive move.

16:27.530 --> 16:29.280
There are so many jobs you can take.

16:29.280 --> 16:31.280
That boss of yours was overbearing.

16:34.080 --> 16:34.700
It's okay.

16:35.390 --> 16:37.650
Things will eventually
sort themselves out.

16:37.650 --> 16:39.080
In this vast city of Beijing,

16:39.080 --> 16:40.010
there must be a job

16:40.010 --> 16:40.670
that I can do.

16:40.670 --> 16:42.000
Exactly, tons of jobs.

16:47.000 --> 16:48.100
Are you free later?

16:48.820 --> 16:49.370
Why?

16:49.840 --> 16:51.500
I'd like to take you to a place.

16:51.600 --> 16:52.730
-Let's go then.
-Go.

16:54.510 --> 16:55.040
Let's go.

17:00.910 --> 17:01.590
Come back!

17:02.100 --> 17:04.109
Did you forget what happened
in the cinema last time?

17:04.109 --> 17:04.750
It's all fine.

17:04.750 --> 17:06.950
I've scouted this place several times.

17:07.000 --> 17:08.200
Come back, Xu Shengli.

17:08.200 --> 17:09.079
It's too risky.

17:09.380 --> 17:09.880
Hurry.

17:10.329 --> 17:11.460
This really is fine.

17:11.500 --> 17:12.980
Don't you see what time it is now?

17:12.980 --> 17:14.460
I'm sure no one will come here.

17:14.460 --> 17:15.109
Besides,

17:16.140 --> 17:17.720
if you are to practice
singing and harmony,

17:17.720 --> 17:18.420
you have to do it

17:18.420 --> 17:19.670
on a stage like this

17:19.720 --> 17:21.849
-for the best effects, right?
-Keep it down.

17:21.849 --> 17:22.790
And this, look.

17:23.069 --> 17:23.930
The spotlight.

17:24.109 --> 17:24.940
Come on, to this spot.

17:24.940 --> 17:25.440
Stand here,

17:25.440 --> 17:26.180
right here.

17:27.720 --> 17:28.920
Now with the spotlight on,

17:28.920 --> 17:30.340
you're the only singer

17:30.500 --> 17:32.500
on this entire stage!

17:33.460 --> 17:35.590
There's one more thing. Wait a second.

17:37.240 --> 17:37.700
This...

17:38.400 --> 17:39.460
I'll put it here.

17:41.330 --> 17:43.460
Then another one here.

17:43.530 --> 17:44.590
What are these?

17:45.350 --> 17:46.810
Recorders. I borrowed them.

17:46.810 --> 17:49.220
These will provide surround sound.

17:50.920 --> 17:52.660
Well, then...

17:52.940 --> 17:55.270
How do you press them both
at the same time?

17:57.790 --> 17:58.590
I will just...

18:01.880 --> 18:02.740
Let me show you.

18:04.220 --> 18:05.020
Are you ready?

18:06.000 --> 18:08.090
Three, two, one.

18:21.810 --> 18:24.960
Wild geese are flying south.

18:25.180 --> 18:28.660
Wild geese are flying south.

18:28.900 --> 18:35.680
The cries of wild geese break my heart.

18:35.830 --> 18:40.830
Though you're only leaving today,

18:41.010 --> 18:45.590
I am already yearning for your return
in spring.

18:46.030 --> 18:52.440
I am already yearning for your return
in spring.

18:54.200 --> 18:56.270
Don't look at me. Look at the audience.

18:56.270 --> 18:57.030
Who's there?

19:00.350 --> 19:01.090
Run, now.

19:01.180 --> 19:02.180
Come on, this way.

19:02.810 --> 19:03.610
Stop running!

19:03.790 --> 19:05.510
Playing "The Phantom of the Opera"
with me, huh?

19:05.510 --> 19:06.310
Stop running!

19:06.810 --> 19:07.650
Halt!

19:12.330 --> 19:13.040
Guo,

19:13.240 --> 19:15.100
pull the rope if you can't take it.

19:15.160 --> 19:15.970
The two of us

19:16.030 --> 19:16.890
will get you up.

19:17.200 --> 19:18.260
Don't act the hero.

19:18.420 --> 19:19.070
I'm fine.

19:30.440 --> 19:30.940
It stinks.

19:30.940 --> 19:33.140
Will he be fine with this stench around?

19:34.500 --> 19:36.330
Guo. Guo!

19:36.440 --> 19:37.440
Are you okay?

19:38.400 --> 19:38.960
Guo!

19:39.160 --> 19:40.160
Not a sound at all.

19:40.160 --> 19:40.890
I wonder why.

19:41.270 --> 19:41.830
Guo!

19:42.050 --> 19:42.810
What's going on?

19:42.810 --> 19:44.180
We're scared for you!

19:44.380 --> 19:45.070
Guo!

19:45.610 --> 19:47.140
Pull him up. Pull him up now.

19:50.550 --> 19:51.590
Get him up.

19:52.070 --> 19:52.470
Quick.

19:52.700 --> 19:53.880
Hang in there, Guo!

19:53.960 --> 19:54.820
Come on, quick.

19:56.720 --> 19:57.450
Help him out.

19:57.920 --> 19:58.940
-Quick.
-Up!

19:59.240 --> 20:01.270
-Up!
-Lean on this.

20:03.030 --> 20:03.590
Guo.

20:08.640 --> 20:09.640
Are you okay, Guo?

20:15.140 --> 20:15.800
Have a rest.

20:17.330 --> 20:18.100
Take it easy.

20:34.640 --> 20:35.970
Have I fainted or what?

20:36.440 --> 20:37.110
Dad!

20:38.880 --> 20:39.330
What?

20:39.400 --> 20:41.500
Dad, get up now.

20:42.590 --> 20:44.440
P-Please get up!

20:45.700 --> 20:46.220
Dad!

20:46.220 --> 20:47.980
Why are the two of you here?

20:47.980 --> 20:49.720
Hurry, get up, Dad!

20:50.740 --> 20:51.160
Dad.

20:51.160 --> 20:52.910
-I smell terrible now.
-Dad!

20:52.940 --> 20:54.080
-I really stink.
-Dad!

20:54.080 --> 20:56.070
-H-Hands off me now.
-Get up!

20:56.180 --> 20:57.090
Hands off me.

21:00.010 --> 21:01.500
My clothes stink.

21:01.700 --> 21:02.360
I smell bad.

21:03.160 --> 21:04.920
-Dad...
-I smell terrible now.

21:05.310 --> 21:06.010
Dad,

21:06.310 --> 21:08.600
stop acting!

21:09.570 --> 21:09.940
I...

21:10.740 --> 21:13.560
Yes, I was just doing...

21:14.030 --> 21:16.690
a scene. A scene.

21:16.980 --> 21:18.640
No, well, I mean...

21:18.750 --> 21:20.210
I was doing field research

21:20.420 --> 21:21.980
for my next role who is...

21:22.030 --> 21:23.570
a sewer cleaner,

21:23.770 --> 21:27.290
just like... Shi Chuanxiang.

21:27.380 --> 21:28.590
-Someone like him.
-Dad!

21:28.590 --> 21:30.830
Dad, stop lying to me.

21:30.850 --> 21:31.650
How am I lying?

21:32.010 --> 21:34.330
Xiaobao, let me wash up first.

21:34.790 --> 21:37.050
Then I'll take you out for mutton hot pot.

21:49.850 --> 21:54.780
I-I was really acting a scene.

21:55.000 --> 21:58.070
Dad, I don't want to eat mutton hot pot.

21:58.310 --> 22:00.530
I want you to go home with me.

22:01.590 --> 22:02.120
Let's go!

22:02.790 --> 22:03.650
What happened?

22:04.030 --> 22:04.760
Hongmei said

22:05.010 --> 22:05.660
she'd like to come

22:05.660 --> 22:08.420
to Beijing to see what your life
has been like in these years.

22:08.420 --> 22:09.700
I told you before

22:09.700 --> 22:12.010
that you couldn't
conceal the truth forever.

22:12.010 --> 22:13.500
Hongmei feels bad for you.

22:13.530 --> 22:15.900
-She cried multiple times in hometown.
-Fine, fine.

22:15.900 --> 22:16.900
I don't blame you.

22:17.270 --> 22:18.880
It's a good thing that they're here.

22:18.880 --> 22:20.400
I can show them around in Beijing

22:20.400 --> 22:21.260
and get Hongmei

22:21.350 --> 22:22.480
medical treatment.

22:22.830 --> 22:23.770
Xiaobao, come here!

22:23.770 --> 22:24.420
Come!

22:24.460 --> 22:25.500
Come on in now.

22:31.510 --> 22:32.510
What do you think?

22:32.790 --> 22:33.720
Let me take this.

22:36.160 --> 22:38.030
Beijing is absolutely huge.

22:38.880 --> 22:39.700
Of course.

22:40.480 --> 22:41.030
Dad,

22:41.290 --> 22:42.610
is here where you live?

22:42.810 --> 22:43.940
The place I live in

22:43.980 --> 22:45.530
is much bigger than this.

22:45.940 --> 22:47.620
But it's too far away.

22:47.980 --> 22:49.040
So we'll stay here,

22:49.330 --> 22:50.930
inside the Second Ring Road.

22:58.980 --> 22:59.420
Hey,

22:59.420 --> 23:00.670
Xiaobao.

23:01.770 --> 23:04.830
Tomorrow, we'll take your mother
to hospital first,

23:05.000 --> 23:06.860
and then go to Tian'anmen Square.

23:06.900 --> 23:07.540
Really?

23:07.740 --> 23:09.780
We'll take some nice photos.

23:09.920 --> 23:10.320
Great.

23:11.740 --> 23:13.380
When school starts,

23:13.530 --> 23:15.790
you can show your classmates the photos.

23:16.110 --> 23:17.940
They'll find you admirable.

23:19.880 --> 23:20.880
It smells so good.

23:22.680 --> 23:24.010
None of your classmates

23:24.050 --> 23:25.850
have been to Tian'anmen Square.

23:26.110 --> 23:27.310
I can do it myself. I can.

23:27.310 --> 23:28.610
Let me... It's dirty.

23:29.000 --> 23:29.920
It's too dirty.

23:30.350 --> 23:31.080
Give it to me.

23:32.250 --> 23:33.050
There it goes.

23:35.440 --> 23:35.970
All good.

23:38.330 --> 23:41.310
I'll go... wash up.

23:44.400 --> 23:44.880
I...

23:46.030 --> 23:51.160
I'll give you a hug after I wash up.

23:54.290 --> 23:56.350
Dad, what were you two talking about?

23:57.050 --> 23:58.780
What could we be talking about?

23:59.050 --> 24:00.850
We were talking about
giving you a beating.

24:00.850 --> 24:02.180
Don't you think I understand what I saw?

24:02.180 --> 24:03.710
What do you understand now?

24:04.180 --> 24:05.270
Sit down.

24:05.420 --> 24:06.500
Get some rest.

24:54.160 --> 24:55.410
Once it gets dark,

24:56.830 --> 24:58.220
you can't read

24:59.090 --> 25:00.610
my lips

25:01.790 --> 25:04.220
or see my gestures.

25:07.240 --> 25:08.340
I really wish

25:09.550 --> 25:10.810
that someday, we could

25:10.850 --> 25:12.500
have a heart-to-heart talk

25:13.920 --> 25:15.720
and whisper in each other's ear.

25:39.810 --> 25:42.420
These days have been really rough for me.

25:43.130 --> 25:44.430
That surgery

25:45.420 --> 25:46.150
can cure you,

25:47.700 --> 25:49.030
but it's too expensive.

25:49.850 --> 25:51.380
I've been so anxious lately

25:52.440 --> 25:54.570
that I've got ulcers all over my mouth.

25:54.880 --> 25:56.590
My throat is inflamed too.

25:58.050 --> 25:59.250
I just hate myself...

26:07.220 --> 26:07.620
for...

26:08.590 --> 26:09.700
not being capable

26:10.480 --> 26:12.210
and not having that much money.

26:13.680 --> 26:15.200
If I could smash up my bones

26:15.200 --> 26:16.900
and sell them,

26:18.030 --> 26:19.660
I would,

26:20.700 --> 26:23.210
so as to get you a cochlear implant.

26:27.430 --> 26:32.930
I want to... sing Yu Opera for you.

26:33.850 --> 26:34.980
When our son grows up

26:35.960 --> 26:36.960
and gets married,

26:37.810 --> 26:40.470
I wish you could also say a few words
on the stage.

26:40.790 --> 26:42.410
If you were able to speak,

26:43.460 --> 26:44.660
you would definitely

26:45.440 --> 26:46.970
be more articulate than me.

26:58.160 --> 26:59.160
You're still up?

27:01.540 --> 27:03.990
Let's go to sleep.

27:05.200 --> 27:05.970
I'll sleep.

27:08.390 --> 27:10.370
Yes, I will.

27:13.770 --> 27:15.160
Gentle pats...

27:17.070 --> 27:17.930
for each other.

27:21.220 --> 27:21.810
Who is it?

27:22.200 --> 27:23.660
This is a room inspection.

27:23.830 --> 27:24.270
What?

27:27.140 --> 27:27.700
It's okay.

27:27.700 --> 27:28.960
Nothing's happening.

27:31.110 --> 27:31.720
It's fine.

27:36.570 --> 27:37.830
Police officers?

27:38.090 --> 27:39.350
Everyone in the room, come out

27:39.350 --> 27:40.590
for a routine inspection.

27:40.590 --> 27:41.940
Do you have your ID cards with you?

27:41.940 --> 27:43.270
Take them out for registration.

27:43.270 --> 27:43.940
Okay, sure.

27:43.980 --> 27:44.400
Got it.

27:51.310 --> 27:52.310
Give it to me.

27:53.830 --> 27:54.950
Officer, our IDs.

28:03.530 --> 28:04.700
Who is this woman?

28:05.000 --> 28:06.220
What's the relationship of you two?

28:06.220 --> 28:07.680
S-She is my wife.

28:08.070 --> 28:10.070
She brought our son here to visit me.

28:11.350 --> 28:12.510
Please show me a marriage certificate.

28:12.510 --> 28:12.850
What?

28:13.310 --> 28:14.770
S-She really is my wife.

28:14.900 --> 28:16.260
Then just show us

28:16.290 --> 28:17.880
some marriage certificate.

28:17.880 --> 28:19.830
Well, neither of us has brought

28:19.900 --> 28:21.300
a marriage certificate.

28:21.400 --> 28:23.050
Don't you have our IDs now?

28:23.400 --> 28:25.190
W-We have been married

28:25.310 --> 28:26.440
for more than 10 years.

28:26.440 --> 28:28.370
L-Look how big our son is.

28:28.660 --> 28:29.790
But how do you prove it?

28:29.790 --> 28:30.660
Officer,

28:30.680 --> 28:31.480
I can prove it.

28:31.530 --> 28:32.530
I'm their child.

28:34.940 --> 28:36.430
Yes, he's our child.

28:40.340 --> 28:40.850
Well,

28:40.850 --> 28:42.180
she's speech impaired.

28:42.200 --> 28:43.140
My mom is saying

28:43.550 --> 28:45.130
that she's my dad's wife

28:45.270 --> 28:46.350
and that I'm her son.

28:46.350 --> 28:47.680
There are rules in place.

28:47.680 --> 28:48.640
For a man and a woman
to sleep in the same room,

28:48.640 --> 28:50.090
they must provide a marriage certificate.

28:50.090 --> 28:51.810
Please understand
that we have our duties to fulfill.

28:51.810 --> 28:52.810
Now get yourselves ready

28:52.810 --> 28:53.790
and go with us.

28:53.960 --> 28:54.490
Don't...

28:55.010 --> 28:56.390
Fine then...

28:56.460 --> 28:59.150
I will get dressed and leave

28:59.270 --> 29:00.800
with you myself. Is it okay?

29:02.330 --> 29:03.210
It's...

29:03.350 --> 29:04.520
It's okay. I...

29:09.550 --> 29:10.410
My mom is saying

29:10.590 --> 29:12.920
that she fell seriously ill
and suddenly went deaf

29:12.920 --> 29:14.300
a few years ago.

29:14.770 --> 29:15.480
Gradually,

29:15.640 --> 29:17.570
she also lost her ability to speak.

29:28.270 --> 29:29.330
But my dad has never

29:29.330 --> 29:30.510
resented her for that.

29:30.510 --> 29:31.550
He still takes good care

29:31.550 --> 29:32.510
of me and her.

29:33.070 --> 29:33.750
My dad

29:33.810 --> 29:34.860
came to Beijing

29:34.960 --> 29:36.620
to earn money exactly for her.

29:39.920 --> 29:40.830
My mom is saying

29:40.960 --> 29:42.920
that my dad only has her as his wife.

29:43.280 --> 29:43.880
And she...

29:43.880 --> 29:45.480
only has my dad as her family.

29:46.330 --> 29:47.160
Hey, Mom,

29:47.850 --> 29:49.790
how could you forget about me?

29:49.810 --> 29:51.270
Aren't I also your family?

29:59.590 --> 30:00.640
My mom is saying

30:00.790 --> 30:01.850
that my dad has been

30:02.050 --> 30:02.770
running

30:02.850 --> 30:04.900
back and forth between Beijing and home.

30:04.900 --> 30:06.310
In order to have her cured,

30:06.310 --> 30:08.510
my dad has been through much suffering.

30:09.440 --> 30:10.170
In addition,

30:10.220 --> 30:12.000
it was not until today that she realized

30:12.000 --> 30:13.760
that my dad had suffered

30:14.050 --> 30:14.900
tremendously

30:15.330 --> 30:16.590
for her and our family.

30:17.220 --> 30:18.140
She considers

30:18.270 --> 30:20.340
herself to be a lucky woman

30:20.570 --> 30:22.050
for meeting such a wonderful man

30:22.050 --> 30:22.950
like my dad.

30:27.380 --> 30:28.490
Officers,

30:28.640 --> 30:30.200
my dad is a good person.

30:31.510 --> 30:33.630
I also just found out today

30:34.270 --> 30:36.470
that my dad,
for the sake of me and my mom,

30:36.530 --> 30:37.930
has done many exhausting

30:38.400 --> 30:39.260
and dirty jobs.

30:42.940 --> 30:43.660
It's okay.

30:43.740 --> 30:45.050
Officer,

30:45.050 --> 30:47.700
can we have a word in private?

30:48.180 --> 30:49.840
Please come with me.

30:54.200 --> 30:54.910
In fact,

30:55.700 --> 30:57.010
I'm a long-term tenant

30:57.110 --> 30:58.710
at the Seasons Change Hostel

30:58.980 --> 31:00.800
in Luogu Hutong.

31:01.090 --> 31:03.840
Officer Tang is quite familiar with me.

31:04.090 --> 31:05.130
I have his number.

31:05.460 --> 31:07.530
Why don't you talk to him?

31:08.550 --> 31:10.200
Now that you and your family have said so,

31:10.200 --> 31:11.570
we'll verify your story
back at the station.

31:11.570 --> 31:11.980
Okay.

31:12.400 --> 31:13.250
If there is a problem,

31:13.250 --> 31:14.250
we will come find you again.

31:14.250 --> 31:15.310
Okay, sure.

31:18.940 --> 31:20.000
Mr. Cui, Mr. Cui!

31:20.150 --> 31:20.550
[Golden Garden at Sunset]

31:21.010 --> 31:22.000
Congratulations!

31:22.000 --> 31:23.090
The director told me

31:23.090 --> 31:23.590
that I could

31:23.590 --> 31:24.880
start getting prepared now.

31:24.880 --> 31:25.550
Does it mean...

31:24.960 --> 31:27.100
[Golden Garden at Sunset]

31:25.720 --> 31:26.980
I've landed the part?

31:27.140 --> 31:27.740
Of course.

31:27.980 --> 31:29.090
He also told me about it just now.

31:29.090 --> 31:29.660
Mr. Cui,

31:29.350 --> 31:33.590
[Golden Garden at Sunset]

31:30.030 --> 31:31.160
if it weren't for you,

31:31.160 --> 31:32.590
I would've given up long ago.

31:32.590 --> 31:33.640
Thank you, Mr. Cui.

31:33.640 --> 31:34.440
Why thank me?

31:34.640 --> 31:36.570
You should thank that guy instead.

31:36.680 --> 31:37.310
Who?

31:38.050 --> 31:40.420
What's the point of hiding the truth
from me?

31:40.420 --> 31:41.950
I'd better not ask too much.

31:43.010 --> 31:44.400
I have things to do later.

31:44.400 --> 31:45.180
So I need to go now.

31:45.180 --> 31:46.480
I just stopped by to see you.

31:46.480 --> 31:47.450
Listen,

31:47.920 --> 31:49.400
this is a great role.

31:49.440 --> 31:50.610
Do take it seriously.

31:50.610 --> 31:51.440
If you rises to fame for it,

31:51.440 --> 31:53.010
you could be the female lead
in the next show, right?

31:51.960 --> 31:54.380
[Golden Garden at Sunset]

31:54.270 --> 31:54.720
Bye!

32:12.490 --> 32:14.880
[Cashier]

32:16.410 --> 32:20.250
[Cashier]

32:37.400 --> 32:38.730
What are you doing here?

32:41.400 --> 32:43.300
Did you get me that part

32:43.510 --> 32:45.240
in the Golden Garden at Sunset?

32:48.140 --> 32:49.150
It was no big deal.

32:49.720 --> 32:50.720
Here's the story.

32:50.750 --> 32:52.000
I helped the filming crew

32:52.000 --> 32:53.440
address some funding problems.

32:53.440 --> 32:54.790
They always felt

32:54.810 --> 32:56.210
that they owed me a favor.

32:56.270 --> 32:58.200
Then I mentioned in passing
that you could be

32:58.200 --> 32:58.960
a good fit.

33:02.160 --> 33:03.580
Do you like the role?

33:04.160 --> 33:05.190
I want to play it.

33:06.440 --> 33:07.850
But I don't want to owe you anything

33:07.850 --> 33:08.580
for this job.

33:13.380 --> 33:14.920
This is not a huge production.

33:14.920 --> 33:16.320
The role is not that good.

33:16.350 --> 33:18.850
I was too embarrassed
to even bring it up to you.

33:18.850 --> 33:19.640
You're overthinking it.

33:19.640 --> 33:21.170
Come on, let's talk inside.

33:37.010 --> 33:40.140
Maybe we don't have to get in there.

33:42.200 --> 33:43.740
Let's catch up another day?

33:46.810 --> 33:48.700
Hey, why do you have to be so stubborn?

33:48.700 --> 33:49.760
Why must you leave?

33:50.250 --> 33:51.720
Let's just fill out a form first.

33:51.720 --> 33:54.140
Filling out a form won't cost a dime.

33:54.500 --> 33:56.780
I'm saying it's free of charge!

33:56.980 --> 33:58.660
The medical fee
is tens of thousands of yuan.

33:58.660 --> 34:02.790
How much suffering will you have to
go through to earn that much?

34:03.480 --> 34:04.740
B-But

34:04.740 --> 34:07.180
didn't the doctor say

34:07.180 --> 34:10.340
that your ears could be fixed?

34:10.420 --> 34:12.230
Can't we just get in the line first?

34:12.230 --> 34:13.380
We'll get in the line

34:13.510 --> 34:13.960
and wait

34:13.960 --> 34:16.980
till we can afford the treatment, alright?

34:17.320 --> 34:20.460
I don't want to hear anything.

34:20.820 --> 34:24.360
I don't want to hear anything!

34:24.480 --> 34:27.179
I just want you to go home with me.

34:27.380 --> 34:28.460
What? Go home?

34:28.880 --> 34:30.000
Why not stay in Beijing?

34:30.000 --> 34:30.820
No way!

34:31.590 --> 34:32.520
You can't leave.

34:32.550 --> 34:34.170
What are you doing?

34:34.300 --> 34:35.840
What are you doing?

34:35.960 --> 34:37.440
Can't you just listen to me?

34:37.440 --> 34:38.800
Just listen to me, okay?

34:38.880 --> 34:39.900
Listen to me!

34:40.110 --> 34:42.050
Can't you just listen to me?

34:42.150 --> 34:44.670
Listen to me! Listen to me!

34:46.610 --> 34:47.790
Xiaobao, come here.

34:47.920 --> 34:48.500
Come.

34:49.150 --> 34:50.780
Tell your mom

34:51.460 --> 34:52.719
your opinion.

34:55.760 --> 34:57.380
How should I put it,

34:57.670 --> 34:58.320
Dad?

34:58.760 --> 35:02.300
I want Mom to get her hearing back.

35:03.000 --> 35:06.670
And I also want to see you every day.

35:28.480 --> 35:29.010
I...

35:38.630 --> 35:41.480
No, we all must stay here.

35:45.760 --> 35:47.490
Why are you calling this place?

35:48.300 --> 35:49.830
Northeasterner said that?

35:50.300 --> 35:52.000
Okay. What's the job then?

35:54.400 --> 35:55.530
It's a piece of cake.

35:56.440 --> 35:58.210
I'll head over now, alright?

35:59.670 --> 36:01.010
Okay. See you in a bit.

36:03.050 --> 36:04.110
Miss, thank you.

36:17.320 --> 36:17.960
Hey,

36:20.010 --> 36:24.340
I need to go to work now.

36:27.050 --> 36:30.190
The two of you get some rest here.

36:31.610 --> 36:35.480
We'll talk about

36:35.920 --> 36:38.130
the medical treatment later.

36:38.510 --> 36:39.130
Okay?

36:45.530 --> 36:46.060
Xiaobao.

36:47.460 --> 36:48.720
I'll be out for a while.

36:49.210 --> 36:50.890
Take good care of your mom.

36:51.110 --> 36:51.690
Got it.

36:54.070 --> 36:56.530
Tomorrow,
I'll take you to the Summer Palace

36:56.710 --> 36:58.550
so you can ride the bronze ox there.

36:58.550 --> 36:59.050
Okay.

37:05.030 --> 37:06.030
I'm leaving then.

37:10.360 --> 37:11.920
Come back early.

37:12.070 --> 37:12.570
Sure.

37:14.880 --> 37:15.520
Off I go.

37:24.880 --> 37:26.120
Sir, how is it going?

37:26.360 --> 37:27.090
Almost done.

37:27.610 --> 37:28.210
Okay.

37:28.530 --> 37:29.690
After you finish,

37:29.730 --> 37:30.940
please conduct a check

37:30.940 --> 37:31.860
on every corner.

37:31.860 --> 37:32.280
Okay.

37:32.750 --> 37:34.400
When it's done, please stay a bit

37:34.400 --> 37:35.360
for a meal here.

37:35.500 --> 37:37.030
I'll cook you some noodles.

37:37.090 --> 37:37.460
Okay.

37:38.260 --> 37:39.790
Actually, no, I can't stay.

37:40.050 --> 37:41.630
My wife and son

37:41.630 --> 37:42.690
are waiting for me.

37:44.070 --> 37:45.800
Can I have the noodles packed?

37:46.210 --> 37:46.760
Sure.

37:47.010 --> 37:48.880
Then please pack a larger portion for me.

37:48.880 --> 37:49.300
Sure!

37:49.500 --> 37:50.800
Y-You go on with your work.

37:50.800 --> 37:51.940
I'll go get the food ready now.

37:51.940 --> 37:52.690
Okay, thanks.

37:52.690 --> 37:53.350
No problem!

37:56.300 --> 37:57.500
Why are you back here?

37:57.510 --> 37:59.440
D-Did you leave something behind?

38:00.000 --> 38:01.150
Leave something behind? I...

38:01.150 --> 38:02.450
I stay in Room 208.

38:02.960 --> 38:04.260
They've checked out.

38:05.530 --> 38:07.500
T-They've checked out?

38:08.450 --> 38:10.280
[Seasons Change Hostel]

38:20.150 --> 38:20.980
Mrs. Jiang,

38:21.130 --> 38:22.530
you are so pretty.

38:22.610 --> 38:24.780
No wonder Mr. Guo misses you every day.

38:26.050 --> 38:27.030
Why isn't Zongbao back yet?

38:27.030 --> 38:29.290
I can't wait to taste this spread of food.

38:29.440 --> 38:30.840
-Zongbao!
-You're back.

38:31.670 --> 38:32.400
Why didn't you

38:32.400 --> 38:34.150
tell us your wife had come for a visit?

38:34.150 --> 38:34.610
This...

38:36.650 --> 38:37.590
Take a seat now.

38:37.590 --> 38:38.710
What's all this gesturing about?

38:38.710 --> 38:39.880
Hurry, take a seat.

38:40.030 --> 38:41.430
Dig in. Start eating now.

38:41.890 --> 38:42.340
I need to wash up.

38:42.340 --> 38:43.780
-Don't go.
-Why wash up at all?

38:43.780 --> 38:45.110
Just sit down and eat.

38:45.110 --> 38:45.610
Quick.

38:45.610 --> 38:47.170
Come on, let me take the bag.

39:01.230 --> 39:02.030
Mrs. Jiang...

39:03.400 --> 39:04.530
Sit down, everyone.

39:04.860 --> 39:05.970
Please sit down.

39:06.230 --> 39:07.460
Mrs. Jiang is asking us to sit.

39:07.460 --> 39:08.320
Be seated then.

39:14.630 --> 39:15.170
Don't drink that much.

39:15.170 --> 39:16.900
-Easy on the drink.
-Easy on it.

39:20.870 --> 39:24.980
[Endeavor]

39:35.170 --> 39:36.290
My mom is saying

39:36.340 --> 39:38.070
that my dad was afraid that we'd see

39:38.070 --> 39:39.550
how hard his life is,

39:39.550 --> 39:40.380
so he didn't bring us

39:40.380 --> 39:41.500
to Beijing.

39:43.110 --> 39:44.170
But now as she's here,

39:44.170 --> 39:46.230
she can actually put her mind at ease.

39:48.130 --> 39:49.210
My mom would like to

39:49.260 --> 39:50.730
thank you all today.

39:53.960 --> 39:55.820
She's saying that she's grateful to you

39:55.820 --> 39:57.820
for taking care of my dad for so long.

40:01.840 --> 40:02.700
My mom is saying

40:02.820 --> 40:04.750
that she really loves this hostel.

40:06.940 --> 40:08.220
She didn't realize

40:08.260 --> 40:09.320
how happily my dad lives here

40:09.320 --> 40:10.950
until she came for a look.

40:15.720 --> 40:17.340
All of you are good people.

40:27.840 --> 40:28.840
A toast to Mrs. Jiang.

40:28.840 --> 40:29.320
Come on.

40:31.900 --> 40:34.360
Xiaobao, what's the gesture
of "thank you"?

40:35.610 --> 40:36.410
Mrs. Jiang...

40:50.950 --> 40:51.500
Drink up!

40:59.110 --> 41:00.500
Sit down. Sit.

41:00.710 --> 41:01.770
Dig in.

41:02.550 --> 41:05.130
My wife is a wonderful cook.

41:05.170 --> 41:05.690
Eat the food

41:05.690 --> 41:06.820
before it gets cold.

41:06.840 --> 41:07.440
What a delicious spread

41:07.440 --> 41:08.880
Mrs. Jiang prepared for us.

41:08.880 --> 41:09.320
Right?

41:09.340 --> 41:11.280
You should've brought

41:11.460 --> 41:12.780
your fantastic wife and son to Beijing

41:12.780 --> 41:13.760
for a gathering with us.

41:13.760 --> 41:14.610
Yeah.

41:15.300 --> 41:15.900
Here, Son.

41:17.300 --> 41:20.260
Mrs. Jiang, Mr. Guo missed you dearly.

41:25.860 --> 41:26.950
That's right.

41:27.260 --> 41:28.730
Whenever Zongbao talks about you,

41:28.730 --> 41:29.940
he beams with joy

41:30.000 --> 41:31.220
and has a lot to say.

41:32.690 --> 41:35.530
W-When have I ever talked about her?

41:35.530 --> 41:36.540
How have you not?

41:36.920 --> 41:38.070
Every night when you talk

41:38.070 --> 41:38.670
in your sleep,

41:38.670 --> 41:40.830
you call Mrs. Jiang's name.

41:41.010 --> 41:41.960
I don't. Do I?

41:41.980 --> 41:42.910
You can ask them.

41:43.010 --> 41:44.270
I-I've heard it too.

41:45.230 --> 41:46.090
You're no good.

41:51.130 --> 41:51.530
What?

41:54.440 --> 41:55.360
It's dirt.

41:55.480 --> 41:56.490
So tasty.

41:57.300 --> 41:59.760
Dad, I'd like to make a toast
to everyone too.

41:59.840 --> 42:00.670
Go ahead then.

42:01.000 --> 42:01.980
Guys, listen,

42:02.440 --> 42:05.290
Xiaobao has a few words to say.

42:05.550 --> 42:06.780
He'd like to make toast

42:06.780 --> 42:08.320
to all of you, just like I did.

42:08.320 --> 42:09.400
A warm welcome for him!

42:09.400 --> 42:11.060
Say a few words then, Xiaobao!

42:11.650 --> 42:13.310
-Come on.
-The floor's yours.

42:13.960 --> 42:15.220
Ladies and gentlemen,

42:15.630 --> 42:16.630
over these years,

42:17.000 --> 42:19.100
my dad has kept telling me

42:19.340 --> 42:22.100
to come to Beijing when I grow up.

42:19.410 --> 42:26.990
[Endeavor]

42:22.550 --> 42:23.860
But I never knew

42:24.230 --> 42:26.700
why I should come to Beijing.

42:27.380 --> 42:29.940
Just now, I realized the reason.

42:30.380 --> 42:32.720
What did you figure out?

42:33.420 --> 42:35.620
It turns out that my dad lives

42:35.840 --> 42:38.080
with a singer, a musician,

42:38.340 --> 42:39.360
a big star,

42:39.840 --> 42:42.070
a great screenwriter who writes for films

42:42.070 --> 42:43.470
and a brilliant painter.

42:44.300 --> 42:45.790
I've never seen these many

42:46.030 --> 42:49.170
prominent figures
in the county or village.

42:50.000 --> 42:52.120
Dad, now I understand

42:52.670 --> 42:54.690
how splendid Beijing is.
